high_descs: Move forward and then turn right to find the stove.
Pick up the pan from the back left burner.
Carry the pan and turn to the left, and face left to the round table.
Place the pan on the table, to the right side.
Pick up an apple from the center of the table.
Place the apple in the pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan to a table and place an apple inside.

high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the stove.
Pick up the metal pan off of the back left burner of the stove.
Turn left and walk over to the round black table.
Put the metal pan on the round black table.
Pick up the closest apple off of the table.
Put the apple on the pan on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple on a pan on a table.
